town milk
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:(in attrib. use) [of farms, farmers and herds] providing milk all year round for town consumption.


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
Region: [none]
